Refine Your Experience Cloud Site with New Customer Identity Features
Get more control over your identity verification process. Give users uninterrupted access across custom apps and Salesforce UIs by bridging an existing access token into a new UI session. Enable Embedded Login.

Where: These changes apply to LWR, Aura, and Visualforce sites accessed through Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
